---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import type84 from "../../assets/type-84.webp";
import interiorType84 from "../../assets/interior_type_84.webp";
---

<div
  class="w-screen h-fit md:h-screen flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-start md:justify-between"
>
  <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 h-fit md:h-full flex flex-col relative">
    <div
      class="w-full h-fit md:h-8/12 flex flex-col relative md:justify-center"
    >
      <div
        class="w-full h-fit font-['Poppins'] py-5 pl-5 pr-10 md:pr-5 pb-5 md:pb-0 text-justify md:text-right text-shadow-sm"
      >
        <p
          class="font-extrabold text-lg/snug md:text-2xl/snug lg:text-3xl/snug"
        >
          <span class="text-yellow-400">Exclusive</span> Boarding House
        </p>
        <p
          class="font-extrabold text-xl/snug md:text-3xl/snug lg:text-4xl/snug mb-1 md:mb-3 text-shadow-sm"
        >
          <span class="text-yellow-400 text-nowrap">Type 84</span>
        </p>
        <p class="text-xs md:text-base lg:text-lg break-keep">
          Memiliki konsep bangunan Jawa Modern, dan terdapat enam kamar tidur
          dengan enam kamar mandi dalam super nyaman. Dilengkapi dengan dapur
          bersama, balkon view pegunungan dan persawahan, hingga mini garden
          untuk meningkatkan kualitas udara di area Rukos tetap sejuk. Semua
          space di desain khusus untuk membuat penghuni Rukos tetap nyaman dan
          aman.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="w-full h-50 md:h-4/12 inline-flex relative pb-5 pl-3 pr-8 md:p-0 items-start">
      <Image
        class="object-bottom-left object-cover h-full w-full rounded-xl md:rounded-3xl md:absolute md:-top-10 md:-left-30"
        src={interiorType84}
        alt="Rumah kost Puri Asthagina."
        decoding="async"
        loading="lazy"
      />
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="relative w-full md:w-1/2 h-full inline-flex pb-20 md:pb-0">
    <Image
      class="w-11/12 h-8/12 md:h-full object-cover object-left rounded-xl md:rounded-3xl mx-2"
      src={type84}
      alt="Rumah kost Puri Asthagina."
      decoding="async"
      loading="lazy"
    />
    <div class="w-full h-full absolute flex flex-col">
      <div
        class="w-full h-1/2 md:h-8/12 z-90 p-10 font-['Poppins'] text-white text-shadow-sm text-4xl font-extrabold inline-flex justify-end"
      >
        <p class="pr-2">Type 84</p>
        <hr class="h-0.5 w-1/6 my-5 bg-white border-0 rounded-sm" />
      </div>
      <div
        class="w-full h-1/3 md:h-4/12 z-90 font-['Poppins'] text-base md:text-xl text-shadow-sm flex flex-col"
      >
        <div
          class="w-fit h-fit bg-white z-100 rounded-2xl pr-10 pl-3 py-5 shadow-2xl absolute -right-5 md:-left-45"
        >
          <div class="border-l-4 border-yellow-400 pl-2">
            <p>6 Kamar Tidur</p>
            <p>6 Kamar Mandi</p>
            <p>Area Parkir</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
